### ============================================================
### 阶段三·第四步 联调测试
### 前置：需要先登录获取 token，设置 Redis 库存
### ============================================================

### 变量
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = <替换为登录返回的 accessToken>

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 0. 准备：通过 Redis CLI 设置 SKU 库存（在容器内执行）
### docker exec -it my-backend-sim-redis-1 redis-cli SET stock:1 100
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 1. 正常下单 — 带 SKU 库存预扣
### 预期：200，库存预扣成功，stock_ledger + outbox_events 各写入一条
### -----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "skuItems": [
    { "skuId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "remark": "库存预扣联调测试"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 2. 库存不足下单
### 先将 Redis stock:999 设为 0:
### docker exec -it my-backend-sim-redis-1 redis-cli SET stock:999 0
### 预期：400，"SKU 999 库存不足"
### -----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": 1, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "skuItems": [
    { "skuId": 999, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 3. 手动触发 Outbox 处理
### 预期：200，返回 { total, sent, failed, errors }
### -----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/outbox/process
Content-Type: application/json

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 4. 再次触发 Outbox（应无新事件）
### 预期：total=0
### -----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/outbox/process
Content-Type: application/json

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 5. 不带 skuItems 的普通下单（向后兼容）
### 预期：200，不触发库存预扣
### -----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": 1, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "remark": "无 SKU 的普通下单"
}
